03:29.296 --> 03:35.388
So imperfect information games is when you don't know a particular thing about the game at any point.

03:35.849 --> 03:38.334
So there is hidden information like in poker.

03:38.795 --> 03:40.759
And the problem is right here,

03:40.739 --> 03:48.811
If you do the same thing for this game right here and you look from player one's perspective and you say, okay, this game is very deep.

