05:10.656 --> 05:14.099
And this is something that alpha zero has no concept on.

05:14.479 --> 05:21.165
For alpha zero, the value of a node only ever depends on what comes downstream.

05:21.297 --> 05:29.389
In imperfect information game, the value of a node also depends on what has happened upstream.

05:29.709 --> 05:32.974
So on the strategy of the upstream events.

05:33.935 --> 05:37.540
And that is, as I said, that is quite important.

05:38.121 --> 05:47.254
Also for AlphaZero, once I have evaluated a game tree and determined the value of a node like this,

